data.description: Well maintained Single family home. Convenient to Randolph AFB and Ft Sam. Outstanding neighborhood, close to shopping malls. Walk to Middle School.  House has tons of extras. Lovely property with great curb appeal, open floor plan, super nice kitchen that overlooks family room, luxury master upstairs that has separate garden tub & shower. Game room, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 living, 2 eating areas.
